<body>
    <h1>T9 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"adbddb3cba0c"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"8032a770328c" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-1.Introduction">1.=
 Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"2e7c8834bd89" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose">1.1 Pu=
rpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"29ae7b28c0a0">This document provides a comprehensive technic=
al overview of the design, implementation, and deployment of the <strong>Po=
werOfMath application</strong> on AWS using two distinct architectural mode=
ls:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"677b9dc43407">
<li local-id=3D"780bdbf3852c">
<p local-id=3D"d4f28a1fa718">Serverless Cloud-Native Architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"663e72f61fe7">
<p local-id=3D"282bf389daa2">Traditional VM-Based (2-Tier) Architecture</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"27979738739e">The objective of this document is to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d767efbe9345">
<li local-id=3D"73b4e217622b">
<p local-id=3D"44eb122be5f1">Demonstrate architectural decision-making</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"f43393f02eac">
<p local-id=3D"4d859314695a">Validate AWS best practices implementation</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"ca007a1ab995">
<p local-id=3D"6ca8b6660b69">Provide deployment reproducibility</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6afaa6324a39">
<p local-id=3D"c9f3a6d93bef">Showcase secure and production-ready configura=
tion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21af70c04084">
<p local-id=3D"9c505b0f9326">Compare operational characteristics between se=
rverless and VM models</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4d622fdcba82">This document is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dba4ed8406d9">
<li local-id=3D"1a3e65ad5fe3">
<p local-id=3D"1c7751cf1e19">Chief Technology Officers (Strategic oversight=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"061d1d8fa33b">
<p local-id=3D"44eca08440ec">Solution Architects (Design evaluation)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"e1a3ce23fa42">
<p local-id=3D"17a3d28b0685">DevOps Engineers (Implementation reference)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"fffdb17ab8b8">
<p local-id=3D"b9b46f67a984">Developers (Integration understanding)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"2d1ed81f62f0">
<p local-id=3D"deb03a981941">Technical Resellers / Partners (Capability dem=
onstration)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2b8a5eabd5de">
<h2 local-id=3D"8d3de5275199" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope">1.2 Scop=
e</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8cd77cba7195">This document covers the complete lifecycle of=
 infrastructure provisioning, deployment, configuration, and security harde=
ning for the PowerOfMath application on AWS.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5781412f9f80">The scope includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5bfe7a50f616">
<li local-id=3D"29b776f643b1">
<p local-id=3D"2ab6b1ac8366">AWS resource provisioning (EC2, Lambda, API Ga=
teway, DynamoDB, S3, CloudFront)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a5c477bb815b">
<p local-id=3D"ea22775d34fb">Application deployment and runtime configurati=
on</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7fb2f521e34c">
<p local-id=3D"88ee7b84530a">Reverse proxy and WSGI server setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fdad104ada5f">
<p local-id=3D"88056b5218ad">SSL/TLS configuration (ACM &amp; Let=E2=80=99s=
 Encrypt)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b12ad800d5a5">
<p local-id=3D"fffda5bc3397">Domain and DNS configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be3e27e3a482">
<p local-id=3D"daae2e4d645a">Secure networking and IAM role configuration</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64ded4af2cba">
<p local-id=3D"57f9c01ff62e">High-level cost and operational considerations=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a0fb4776a8e">
<p local-id=3D"a407c26c864a">Architectural comparison between Serverless an=
d VM models</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3af18597293e">Out of scope:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5a429093e311">
<li local-id=3D"694f7de69ba5">
<p local-id=3D"e7003571e910">CI/CD automation (not part of project requirem=
ents)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4df602293d50">
<p local-id=3D"1e1d82233828">Infrastructure as Code (Terraform/CloudFormati=
on)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e6dcdef060e">
<p local-id=3D"f0577ec580ea">Enterprise monitoring stacks (Prometheus/Grafa=
na)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7cdb3be25d93">
<p local-id=3D"c42657022b3f">Multi-region failover</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b752c2020736">The deployment focuses on production-grade bas=
eline implementation within the defined 5-hour time constraint.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e07f4d2a389e">
<h1 local-id=3D"a58103ad50ce" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDevOps=
Project">2. Overview of DevOps Project</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"2c07612a9df1" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition">2.1=
 Definition</h2>
<p local-id=3D"99b630729e01">DevOps is a set of practices that integrates s=
oftware development and IT operations to enable continuous delivery, automa=
tion, infrastructure reliability, and rapid deployment cycles.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c69e40a4b647">In this project, DevOps principles were applie=
d to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ea45e1169797">
<li local-id=3D"e950f43e374f">
<p local-id=3D"e7c99163be69">Automate service management using systemd</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"65930a6e5bc8">
<p local-id=3D"ea457c71ce02">Enable scalable serverless compute via AWS Lam=
bda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4fc5bac9083f">
<p local-id=3D"8fef243a5846">Implement secure HTTPS access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f02299081e9">
<p local-id=3D"f33b9eca036e">Separate frontend and backend layers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"54769d0fae58">
<p local-id=3D"71dd32e30cb8">Apply cloud-native scalability models</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e8d12802970">
<p local-id=3D"0a9d923452ea">Reduce operational overhead</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e9b4a2b20a27">The solution demonstrates two operational mode=
ls:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"6a708666369b">
<li local-id=3D"b1bd6e69087e">
<p local-id=3D"54b2a2875757">Event-driven serverless architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"86b049a5b4d4">
<p local-id=3D"31392db5c25d">Persistent compute-based VM architecture</p></=
li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"c38d1bb45fa2">This dual deployment enables comparative analy=
sis of scaling behavior, operational overhead, cost model, and maintenance =
complexity.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6934f79394aa">
<h2 local-id=3D"0d99ff4ccb33" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-2.2AWSWell-Archite=
ctedFrameworkAlignment">2.2 AWS Well-Architected Framework Alignment</h2>
<p local-id=3D"33a41e159c17">The solution aligns with the AWS Well-Architec=
ted Framework across six pillars:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"7f19dfd06e8c" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-1.OperationalExcel=
lence">1. Operational Excellence</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c5bd2c45e7df">
<li local-id=3D"4db842c55a40">
<p local-id=3D"ba5614abba1b">Structured deployment process</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"79765cbf703e">
<p local-id=3D"73be40ebe526">systemd-managed Gunicorn service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"487d6e5d4fd1">
<p local-id=3D"61388674f64f">Automated SSL renewal (Certbot)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e4f5ee1f2c2e">
<p local-id=3D"28317100af42">Clear service separation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39009afce57e">
<p local-id=3D"6129202c6a14">Documented deployment steps</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"e4fb91128b5c" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-2.Security">2. Sec=
urity</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"b5b1d85f8da9">
<li local-id=3D"54a2db70d17b">
<p local-id=3D"add561c0c57a">IAM role-based access for Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"699b6884ba30">
<p local-id=3D"426f98efcb26">Principle of least privilege for DynamoDB acce=
ss</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f8d2c0d2070">
<p local-id=3D"29652be2dd12">HTTPS enforced on both architectures</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"24d0d32a2191">
<p local-id=3D"d90829b9fb10">Reverse proxy isolation of backend services</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"367a939011e3">
<p local-id=3D"d3c9fd84b05b">No direct exposure of application server ports=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3571a3941fb">
<p local-id=3D"6bac35887f08">Domain-based secured access</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8ed3b64e46fd" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-3.Reliability">3. =
Reliability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2a070de8d83c">
<li local-id=3D"d8761f64d91d">
<p local-id=3D"5a675afa2510">CloudFront global edge distribution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"568df338d26d">
<p local-id=3D"46b49fab4ffb">Lambda auto-scaling behavior</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"911d303e2853">
<p local-id=3D"43d011cf41ec">Gunicorn multi-worker architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81b77b14adbf">
<p local-id=3D"a38f56d0be71">Nginx reverse proxy stability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e44f1ba41fc5">
<p local-id=3D"ebbca2e038f2">Service auto-restart via systemd</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"af6524e2952c" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-4.PerformanceEffic=
iency">4. Performance Efficiency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c7d1927ae130">
<li local-id=3D"fb41174304c0">
<p local-id=3D"f6797222bb1b">Serverless compute auto-scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"515b369de22a">
<p local-id=3D"c0fe30eea933">CDN caching through CloudFront</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b403f0af9505">
<p local-id=3D"57796f673c08">Unix socket communication for Gunicorn</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"b46c984319eb">
<p local-id=3D"4076dede47f4">Optimized worker configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"61c736138994" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-5.CostOptimization=
">5. Cost Optimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a78aed6afd64">
<li local-id=3D"d07dcef4018b">
<p local-id=3D"969a6b0ab3d9">AWS Free Tier resource utilization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"454338516eb3">
<p local-id=3D"d30f6d70e2c9">Pay-per-use Lambda billing model</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"246f652dc60e">
<p local-id=3D"f29defea9b16">No over-provisioned infrastructure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc45f4a072a4">
<p local-id=3D"66230b8e6b58">Lightweight compute footprint</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c1a9e8f00c3">
<p local-id=3D"d930a51013ae">Minimal persistent resources</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"e5e59e512810" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-6.Sustainability">=
6. Sustainability</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"dc9dd6db9634">
<li local-id=3D"df1cd0900b50">
<p local-id=3D"c81388f343ca">On-demand compute (Lambda)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d686634dd8bd">
<p local-id=3D"ad3c3fccb651">Reduced idle resource usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8638ffe3b6a9">
<p local-id=3D"176443dda31d">Efficient resource allocation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ad3a771eb55">
<p local-id=3D"1303bdc4b1d3">Scalable architecture minimizing waste</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"76bd33f45e02">
<h2 local-id=3D"29c98db3d74e" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObjecti=
ves">2.3 Goals and Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"872c7e852343">The primary goals of this implementation were:=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d4ad9612b0ef">
<li local-id=3D"2cbe248ae1ee">
<p local-id=3D"6e47fb31f26e">Deploy the application using two distinct AWS =
architectural models</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"569fceea55c0">
<p local-id=3D"3e7c31c7073e">Implement secure HTTPS communication for both =
deployments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"362ca61173d9">
<p local-id=3D"5f223c5cbece">Enable public accessibility via domain-based r=
outing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e01ddf59dd6f">
<p local-id=3D"c4be742c2263">Maintain production-grade separation of concer=
ns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"53f7dfcea7ea">
<p local-id=3D"c142f1924e4d">Ensure resilience across restarts and reboots<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bd3f26da822">
<p local-id=3D"37310f1df838">Provide architectural comparison for operation=
al evaluation</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"793c36ccab61">
<h2 local-id=3D"51ad44225b12" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-2.4ConstraintsandA=
ssumptions">2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"27c48749a2a1" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-Constraints">Const=
raints</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d6e6ace3bf08">
<li local-id=3D"4f54ffdf3cc2">
<p local-id=3D"e9e8f314b9f4">5-hour implementation window</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"edc3c110a8ff">
<p local-id=3D"3b3cfdf05975">Limited budget (Free-tier usage)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7fd10ad15c9c">
<p local-id=3D"c3d618118d8b">No Infrastructure-as-Code requirement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f8e12a668253">
<p local-id=3D"7c643618f722">No CI/CD requirement</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c15fbd663e8">
<p local-id=3D"f431b172b73f">Single-engineer execution</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8d942b862389" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-Assumptions">Assum=
ptions</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"dad40d8fd0e7">
<li local-id=3D"6d4932c248a0">
<p local-id=3D"a82f4652970f">AWS account access available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bca12a6e0bc">
<p local-id=3D"b4b9944e0f75">DNS control delegated to domain administrator<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df2a6e0498a3">
<p local-id=3D"dc33d3b0548c">Public internet exposure allowed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"94d25ad28d94">
<p local-id=3D"cfd255cd1890">Free-tier compute capacity sufficient for work=
load</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"368e3f51b733" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-3.ArchitectureandI=
nfrastructure">3. Architecture and Infrastructure</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"da752cc686f4">
<h3 local-id=3D"2ca94b0d63a8" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-AWSArchitectureDia=
gram">AWS Architecture Diagram</h3><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-=
wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D=
"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"diagram-export-3-5-2026-1_2=
6_41-AM-20260304-195831.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"26d7c42f=
6aafcde59f0251732a3c8d6cca68110ef25c0263d568edf556927bd2" data-image-src=3D=
"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1818984526/diagram-=
