<h1 local-id=3D"dc1cd4bac9d9" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-3.1ServerlessDeplo=
ymentImplementation">3.1 Serverless Deployment Implementation</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"88e305453795">
<h2 local-id=3D"7c1e99760fa2" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP1=E2=80=94IAMR=
oleCreationforLambda">STEP 1 =E2=80=94 IAM Role Creation for Lambda</h2>
<p local-id=3D"06b019c96054">An IAM execution role was created to allow AWS=
 Lambda to securely interact with DynamoDB.</p>
<p local-id=3D"55516680ef86">The role followed the principle of least privi=
lege and included:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b64e9c3874dd">
<li local-id=3D"1bfccc12f761">
<p local-id=3D"0547b455209c">AWSLambdaBasicExecutionRole (for CloudWatch lo=
gging)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"933761eb132e">
<p local-id=3D"ba6ca47a131a">DynamoDB access permissions (PutItem)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"41079d85a7b4">This ensures the function can log execution ev=
ents and store computation results securely.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e21973b723a3"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260302-194128.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"060c738ed45f700124594e3c74ee88d3a7d389f9b3=
45ba8ce18ddf414cc278b2" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1818984526/image-20260302-194128.png?version=3D1&amp;=
modificationDate=3D1772480497668&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-he=
ight=3D"756" data-width=3D"1704" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-l=
inked-resource-id=3D"1821310989" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-li=
nked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"ima=
ge-20260302-194128.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki"=
 data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-conta=
iner-id=3D"1818984526" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-me=
dia-id=3D"45bffe39-d666-4f8a-90a1-959175c5bf70" data-media-type=3D"file" he=
ight=3D"207"></span>
<p local-id=3D"505d9204c616">Figure 1: IAM Role with Least-Privilege Access=
 for Lambda</p>
<hr local-id=3D"bcd1ae11cfe2">
<h2 local-id=3D"0a0e8f07a345" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP2=E2=80=94Dyna=
moDBTableCreation">STEP 2 =E2=80=94 DynamoDB Table Creation</h2>
<p local-id=3D"529a8d26e748">A DynamoDB table named <code>PowerOfMathDataba=
se</code> was created to store computation results.</p>
<p local-id=3D"e6717e919c59">Configuration:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3db5e5044ee7">
<li local-id=3D"4a4c124d3d9d">
<p local-id=3D"5806c2afa1eb">Partition Key: ID (String)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cde91bdfb2c">
<p local-id=3D"140665cbc5fc">On-demand capacity mode (cost optimized)</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"b9f2d2282b0f">
<p local-id=3D"93dd3808afdc">No secondary indexes (not required for workloa=
d)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5c0b291c7ea8">This enables serverless persistence without pr=
ovisioning database servers.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"64296bac1b52"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260302-194953.png" width=
