<hr local-id=3D"cd986d1dd1cf">
<h2 local-id=3D"65e601cd808d" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP3=E2=80=94Lamb=
daFunctionDeployment">STEP 3 =E2=80=94 Lambda Function Deployment</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"19973cd21fcf" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-WhatYouWrite">What=
 You Write</h3>
<p local-id=3D"39c55fd322c9">A Python-based Lambda function was created to:=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cab9b242a726">
<li local-id=3D"4d8fa5533c58">
<p local-id=3D"2c1bd701712c">Accept base and exponent values</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"883f7c368d15">
<p local-id=3D"66a2821b40f2">Perform mathematical computation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"343535078c30">
<p local-id=3D"b7a398aa9e94">Store results in DynamoDB</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d4a765c53f6">
<p local-id=3D"2b5b27d0ef10">Return structured JSON response</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a7569638dd91">Configuration:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fd872473dd3e">
<li local-id=3D"aa40ef48c896">
<p local-id=3D"90443ed41e1f">Runtime: Python 3.x</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7dddad66fdbe">
<p local-id=3D"1a9f4a988d76">IAM Role: Attached execution role</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb3e42bd1535">
<p local-id=3D"e7fc8b3c7e07">Integrated with DynamoDB</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c2ad271b97af">This allows fully event-driven backend process=
ing.</p>
