<hr local-id=3D"79fe9565c592">
<h2 local-id=3D"a352693ff219" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP4=E2=80=94APIG=
atewayIntegration">STEP 4 =E2=80=94 API Gateway Integration</h2>
<p local-id=3D"af762d70bfef">An HTTP API was created using API Gateway to e=
xpose the Lambda function as a REST endpoint.</p>
<p local-id=3D"2ff193a5975f">Configuration:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7e0d15846ed0">
<li local-id=3D"6cf369a265aa">
<p local-id=3D"3819f6f89494">Route: POST /calculate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4aba15614bb">
<p local-id=3D"6d37d2034ad1">Integration type: Lambda Proxy Integration</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"eb0adb6154f2">
<p local-id=3D"78f347ca93c3">CORS enabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b84c7d3d971">
<p local-id=3D"26a185d32763">Public endpoint generated</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ba52b0695998">This enables secure public access to the serve=
rless backend.</p>
