<h2 local-id=3D"c3a15d8aab5f" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP5=E2=80=94S3St=
aticWebsiteHosting">STEP 5 =E2=80=94 S3 Static Website Hosting</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7ced45672e59">An S3 bucket was created to host the frontend =
HTML application.</p>
<p local-id=3D"1143eaa24c0c">Configuration:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"082d314054a8">
<li local-id=3D"8d3513fe5f30">
<p local-id=3D"ea5e0904af16">Static website hosting enabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfd676aedc3e">
<p local-id=3D"3b43297172e6">Public access configured for read-only</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"f3c5cc0e4d8c">
<p local-id=3D"45e53c93c824">index.html configured as default document</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2468bf9c935d">This separates frontend from backend for bette=
r scalability.</p>
