<hr local-id=3D"aeba231bc20c">
<h2 local-id=3D"bc81801a9203" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP6=E2=80=94Clou=
dFrontDistributionSetup">STEP 6 =E2=80=94 CloudFront Distribution Setup</h2=
>
<p local-id=3D"6fc768eb1d9f">A CloudFront distribution was configured to:</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"9453b76ccc3f">
<li local-id=3D"9edaf679da0d">
<p local-id=3D"1556e61d9435">Serve the S3 frontend globally</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4da4170969b2">
<p local-id=3D"434d065f8c69">Improve latency via edge caching</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"072563d1e7ef">
<p local-id=3D"1abf669bc3ab">Enable HTTPS using ACM certificate</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6e05906238e0">CloudFront acts as a secure global entry point=
.</p>
