SLCertificate">STEP 7 =E2=80=94 ACM SSL Certificate</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3fed47f829d8">An ACM certificate was requested in the us-eas=
t-1 region for CloudFront compatibility.</p>
<p local-id=3D"587d699c7915">DNS validation was completed via CNAME records=
.</p>
<p local-id=3D"29faefd20e8a">After validation, HTTPS was enabled for the cu=
stom domain.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6147d5350fa1"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260304-173457.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"55e443d9eb4cd083a7de1b229642668f237b0b9ac2=
6fb5e3200f75eaecec59dd" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
