t</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"dc6069f3b6ec" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP8=E2=80=94Clou=
dFrontDomainAccessandApplicationVerification">STEP 8 =E2=80=94 CloudFront D=
omain Access and Application Verification</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6ade3fde8a49">After configuring the CloudFront distribution =
and associating the custom domain with the ACM SSL certificate, the static =
web application was accessed securely over HTTPS.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4d12b5b29e7f">The CloudFront distribution domain and the con=
figured custom domain were used to verify successful deployment of the fron=
tend application hosted in Amazon S3.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8416de0eb9b0">During testing:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f03c56e691c7">
<li local-id=3D"41534cfeb7c4">
<p local-id=3D"d753441b3786">The application interface loaded successfully =
through the CloudFront endpoint.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2a4bcc1d29de">
<p local-id=3D"e86e02baf823">User inputs for the base and exponent values w=
ere accepted through the web interface.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb3eeb7380a7">
<p local-id=3D"aecaaa734260">The calculation request was sent to the API Ga=
teway endpoint.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"706ba15780c8">
<p local-id=3D"80258c8a30f6">The Lambda function executed the computation a=
nd returned the result.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c711b9a0411">
<p local-id=3D"c0a061a199e7">The result was displayed to the user through t=
he frontend application.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b8c77d7524b8">This step confirms that the <strong>entire ser=
verless architecture =E2=80=94 S3, CloudFront, API Gateway, Lambda, and Dyn=
amoDB =E2=80=94 is functioning correctly as an integrated system.</strong><=
/p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper con=
fluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image=
