<h1 local-id=3D"2593b1317a0d" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-3.2TraditionalVM-B=
asedDeploymentImplementation">3.2 Traditional VM-Based Deployment Implement=
ation</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"4702d042c617">
<h1 local-id=3D"d01bb61a4b82" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-STEP1=E2=80=94EC2I=
nstanceProvisioning">STEP 1 =E2=80=94 EC2 Instance Provisioning</h1>
<p local-id=3D"236c6b72be39">An Ubuntu-based EC2 instance was launched to h=
ost the traditional VM deployment of the PowerOfMath application.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b99b4430e410">Configuration included:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c61f1bd59360">
<li local-id=3D"7cd028f77e55">
<p local-id=3D"745b74fff617">Public IPv4 address enabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"07a5fc1340c8">
<p local-id=3D"f07fba890968">Security Group allowing:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9c412c6b46f8">
<li local-id=3D"db34dd50e28a">
<p local-id=3D"17e5e3434890">Port 22 (SSH)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dbbcd34fa5e8">
<p local-id=3D"67cfc9f1b2eb">Port 80 (HTTP)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5492744b29ec">
<p local-id=3D"70dc932c8804">Port 443 (HTTPS)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae5c643bf2d8">
<p local-id=3D"6c584f0f56b9">Instance type: Free-tier eligible</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f9a6cb1cc42">
<p local-id=3D"4b1802fb6518">Key pair authentication enabled</p></li>
</ul>
