<h1 local-id=3D"21a6ac89aa9b" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentPract=
ices">4. Development Practices</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"f25bc3b561eb">
<h2 local-id=3D"e16cf44d3994" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-4.1VersionControl"=
>4.1 Version Control</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ae2ddbda4b6a">The PowerOfMath application source code is mai=
ntained in a centralized GitHub repository:</p>
<p local-id=3D"bb1aef2cede2">Repository: pushkar-iamops/powerofmath</p>
<p local-id=3D"ebfa88e6adef">For this implementation, the deployment proces=
s focused on infrastructure provisioning rather than source code developmen=
t.</p>
<p local-id=3D"23b41f45cd24">The application code was used as a stable base=
 version for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"527b54669416">
<li local-id=3D"415bee54fb40">
<p local-id=3D"43cdcce6ed8d">Serverless deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d63c61c3e7e">
<p local-id=3D"cafaa7dec18d">EC2 VM-based deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ec500e9c442e">No structural changes to core application logi=
c were required.</p>
<p local-id=3D"90b2f1db05ac">Version control strategy:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f93a5d439ddb">
<li local-id=3D"c03e9e8941bc">
<p local-id=3D"9e080544eea1">Centralized repository management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55e81bfb2420">
<p local-id=3D"2651076bafc6">Stable baseline deployment model</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df8041d85f3f">
<p local-id=3D"3873e4cc5034">Single-branch deployment workflow</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d17f7088ccc4">Due to project constraints and limited timelin=
e (5 hours), advanced branching strategies and release tagging were not imp=
lemented.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"951fc5871816">
<h2 local-id=3D"4db3a8642d1e" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-4.2ContinuousInteg=
ration">4.2 Continuous Integration</h2>
<p local-id=3D"11e6f3289969">This project did not require implementation of=
 a CI/CD pipeline.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d7f7f2dbfcf9">Deployment steps were performed manually throu=
gh:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c327d6d73746">
<li local-id=3D"7824d54afa6d">
<p local-id=3D"95b0f8036793">AWS Console configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4da6c90afb6c">
<p local-id=3D"00ecdb94c083">EC2 terminal configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"384aacd5c1a6">
<p local-id=3D"c8d02768f448">Direct service setup (Nginx, Gunicorn, systemd=
)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7973f4112238">However, the current architecture fully suppor=
ts future CI/CD integration using:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b875d338d169">
<li local-id=3D"ddad3313974f">
<p local-id=3D"016b1f6ab207">GitHub Actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"632033b35eec">
<p local-id=3D"63845d8e30f3">Jenkins</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed632cbf4b1c">
<p local-id=3D"bde757eda5fc">AWS CodePipeline</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"bd5b0486ce0a">The separation of frontend, backend, and infra=
structure components enables easy pipeline automation in future iterations.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"f2d36a51ff08">
<h1 local-id=3D"f86add3d49ef" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-4.3AutomatedTestin=
g">4.3 Automated Testing</h1>
<p local-id=3D"6ca88b83dbc8">Automated testing was not implemented as part =
of the project requirements.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5bca25c9410f">Functional validation was performed through:</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"2de9023363c9">
<li local-id=3D"4d70b3b8becf">
<p local-id=3D"be4d606a35a2">API testing using curl</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a2f3032101e6">
<p local-id=3D"f27b0a73e399">Browser-based frontend validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c7c93c00c8bd">
<p local-id=3D"f1ecfb42af00">DynamoDB record verification</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0b9f4cf0d5c">
<p local-id=3D"18f872eb28ff">HTTPS verification checks</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e897330a5ef0">Future enhancements could include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8a64ef806be5">
<li local-id=3D"de2498d59505">
<p local-id=3D"6405feab9b2d">Pytest unit tests</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25cb4c8207c5">
<p local-id=3D"142dbb355f3b">API integration tests</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a0d2b4bf79d6">
<p local-id=3D"348d7b9574b1">CI-triggered test execution</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c2ce08161907">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">curl -X=
 POST https://ec2.powerofmath-karna.pushkar.cloud/calculate \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{"base":"2","exponent":"3"}'</pre>
</div>
</div><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
