<p local-id=3D"7368ce27b8cf">This shows backend works independently of fron=
tend.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"b7aa735e0219">
<h1 local-id=3D"08d0cd22f473" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-4.4CodeQualityandA=
nalysis">4.4 Code Quality and Analysis</h1>
<p local-id=3D"b7f1642ea0a3">Code quality practices included:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"63c961216da3">
<li local-id=3D"cc9fbfd6c2d5">
<p local-id=3D"0baa8db6d66d">Structured Flask application design</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"56cbd155d5b6">
<p local-id=3D"4b0e360ea77c">Separation of routing and business logic</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"7f342acc5a5a">
<p local-id=3D"c75eb309aca4">Use of WSGI production server (Gunicorn)</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"a35186fe5908">
<p local-id=3D"c15c4d816bdd">Reverse proxy isolation (Nginx)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"494e65b22947">Formal static code analysis tools were not imp=
lemented due to time constraints but can be integrated in future iterations=
.</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"6c1345d4b71a" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-5.DeploymentandRel=
easeManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"f986dd7227c5">
<h1 local-id=3D"bdc70f895eeb" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentStrat=
egy">5.1 Deployment Strategy</h1>
<p local-id=3D"cab55d8604f4">The application was deployed using two indepen=
dent strategies aligned with their respective architecture models.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"bd19d74f523e" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessDeployme=
ntStrategy">Serverless Deployment Strategy</h3>
<p local-id=3D"50e871d670f9">The serverless architecture follows an event-d=
riven deployment model:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed3580a53191">
<li local-id=3D"008826ef0724">
<p local-id=3D"a5e5254bd94a">Frontend hosted on S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44c5a52d2a39">
<p local-id=3D"4eae37463f9e">Backend deployed as AWS Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b65ac1b887f0">
<p local-id=3D"8222401f0ecb">API exposed via API Gateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"70c6834c7e0b">
<p local-id=3D"cc2b402d7c1b">Global access via CloudFront</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e42c532f445a">
<p local-id=3D"cfbce69bb4a6">HTTPS enabled through ACM</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"039c204bbb9c">Deployment Characteristics:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e1511c7b0a32">
<li local-id=3D"342351c4fbdf">
<p local-id=3D"f97e4b75f729">No server management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb767b398fa2">
<p local-id=3D"056932c49c75">Automatic scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c22bde2f73e">
<p local-id=3D"a22d7e99003c">Zero-downtime backend updates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"11c313c273d2">
<p local-id=3D"b6b08b76bf00">Managed infrastructure</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e01bd17c1c3e">Lambda updates are atomic and do not interrupt=
 existing executions.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"50daa8d4e5a4">
<h3 local-id=3D"b30bef0a7fcd" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-TraditionalVM-Base=
dDeploymentStrategy">Traditional VM-Based Deployment Strategy</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7ff332c388de">The VM-based deployment follows a 2-tier archi=
tecture:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e4da8978e092">
<li local-id=3D"ea82198c4e5b">
<p local-id=3D"f4f444d50758">Nginx reverse proxy for HTTP/HTTPS handling</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"9cac98b7ae25">
<p local-id=3D"8f7c4d5a56a6">Gunicorn as WSGI server</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9fe485976d35">
<p local-id=3D"1356db078354">Flask application backend</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c482264e13c2">
<p local-id=3D"a36aba08613b">systemd service management</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"87947c9964c6">Deployment Characteristics:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"56e068819b07">
<li local-id=3D"2c69bb7be57b">
<p local-id=3D"410b0cc7269e">Manual configuration control</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80e42a1d6261">
<p local-id=3D"3cc06e1c1906">Persistent server runtime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2fe166196eb3">
<p local-id=3D"134a0c7eda06">Reverse proxy isolation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d96472242de5">
<p local-id=3D"85620c17bfb9">Controlled service lifecycle</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7097b9d01417">Application stability is ensured via:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4dafe6c74037">
<li local-id=3D"b39dd671b2ae">
<p local-id=3D"ab4ca975d109">systemd auto-restart</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e41d5e8f17d6">
<p local-id=3D"a00c0027639e">Nginx reverse proxy validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9bbfce53adb1">
<p local-id=3D"52e62421fe5b">SSL certificate automation via Certbot</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2c32b0752a41">
<p local-id=3D"4b9b539bc721">This dual-architecture deployment enables oper=
ational comparison between serverless elasticity and persistent compute man=
agement models.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"866a993910b7">
<h1 local-id=3D"ffe236316162" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-5.2ConfigurationMa=
nagement">5.2 Configuration Management</h1>
<p local-id=3D"132215645d75">Configuration management was handled using nat=
ive AWS and Linux service configurations.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"bcc1b4cab0b8" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessConfigur=
ation">Serverless Configuration</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"80cabff6abba">
<li local-id=3D"c82cba568c69">
<p local-id=3D"9f500063593b">IAM roles for secure service access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8113e5663247">
<p local-id=3D"cff4738cee9d">Lambda environment runtime configuration</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"2bf67c23f8b5">
<p local-id=3D"bfdc98ce9e2c">API Gateway route configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c36b5bfb10ac">
<p local-id=3D"a1e3ffeda15f">CloudFront origin and behavior settings</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"932ea76371cf">
<p local-id=3D"38cc66408f94">ACM certificate attachment</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"7f585218715c" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-VM-BasedConfigurat=
ion">VM-Based Configuration</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1b5171ba8792">
<li local-id=3D"67a684622860">
<p local-id=3D"083dfbcfb76f">systemd service file for Gunicorn</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d30dced86966">
<p local-id=3D"938da3d0701e">Nginx reverse proxy configuration file</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"54ee4b8febe4">
<p local-id=3D"3c1e63e18162">Unix socket binding between Gunicorn and Nginx=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e43042ce6fb">
<p local-id=3D"c58f92f23b95">Security Group firewall rules</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb87a22057bd">
<p local-id=3D"26f59c32a8d4">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt certificate auto-renew c=
onfiguration</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2e5d86e8190b">All configurations are reproducible and docume=
nted step-by-step.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"48c7f0131f23">
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ca=
t /etc/systemd/system/powerofmath.service</pre>
</div>
</div><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper =
confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image im=
age-center" alt=3D"image-20260302-203525.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy=
" src=3D"9b114c741cc831a7426c87ad39cfd8d725e895bc11737b540e6d0d5a831cecfb" =
data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/18=
18984526/image-20260302-203525.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D17724=
83732828&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"348" data-width=
=3D"1225" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"18=
21900835" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"a=
ttachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260302-203525.png"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-c=
ontent-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1818984526" =
data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-media-id=3D"81e84e17-4910=
-4417-82d1-fb2f74151d6e" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"133"></span>
<p local-id=3D"b990782ef57a">This proves structured configuration managemen=
t.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"fbf0ed085ed0">
<h1 local-id=3D"f9e4e396bc81" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-5.3ContinuousDeliv=
ery/Deployment">5.3 Continuous Delivery / Deployment</h1>
<p local-id=3D"6742e0fa2107">Since CI/CD was not required, we frame careful=
ly.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3884b5675d9f">This implementation did not include automated =
CI/CD pipelines due to project scope and time constraints.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6eca75159b17">Deployment was executed manually in a controll=
ed sequence:</p>
<p local-id=3D"63cd5611fbbc">Serverless:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"efccb7d22e34">
<li local-id=3D"8e85a88c4ec2">
<p local-id=3D"a2eff3c9c88c">IAM Role creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19fd69fd98b8">
<p local-id=3D"e94616a89d60">DynamoDB table setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37ddc2780510">
<p local-id=3D"cea9095b9970">Lambda deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e970a5af43d9">
<p local-id=3D"a6103d4c1b65">API Gateway integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"60b075d78d3d">
<p local-id=3D"15315dca0e52">S3 static hosting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe12f937c156">
<p local-id=3D"b1514882f254">CloudFront configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d8f20978b11">
<p local-id=3D"0e6b11f1789c">ACM certificate validation</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"33f0b7a4ca10">VM-Based:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e7d2edee27b8">
<li local-id=3D"7a845b4daafa">
<p local-id=3D"261412770c5e">EC2 provisioning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7f70d01ea63">
<p local-id=3D"98943900b62c">Runtime installation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"528fbea19e3f">
<p local-id=3D"8b9efc58e1b5">Application deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8fb0a0aa636f">
<p local-id=3D"c31c99221cba">Gunicorn configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"808a4104f923">
<p local-id=3D"6dacf3563d02">systemd service creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"02077da33049">
<p local-id=3D"31b1989dc73f">Nginx reverse proxy setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f03ce4a5d2c">
<p local-id=3D"bcaae1581d26">DNS mapping</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2727098a6266">
<p local-id=3D"31ed96a8a99f">SSL configuration</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"bfc1a381f786">The architecture supports future automation vi=
a:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"422bf9c5ae9a">
<li local-id=3D"295a54466d0a">
<p local-id=3D"f450d72897b9">GitHub Actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5812b5ff051f">
<p local-id=3D"39a28b6b11a0">Jenkins</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d147d83f87c">
<p local-id=3D"f442904d88b2">AWS CodePipeline</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4598b1635e41">The separation of concerns allows seamless pip=
eline integration without structural redesign.</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"e121e8bae430" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-6.MonitoringandInc=
identManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"ae463cf61117">
<h2 local-id=3D"b2380afa5d0b" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-6.1MonitoringTools=
andMetrics">6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</h2>
<p local-id=3D"35ef1bbf72a1">Monitoring for this deployment relied on nativ=
e service-level observability and manual validation due to project scope co=
nstraints.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"70dc68931083" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessMonitori=
ngApproach">Serverless Monitoring Approach</h3>
<p local-id=3D"f58d05de100b">Although AWS provides CloudWatch integration b=
y default for Lambda and API Gateway, active monitoring dashboards and alar=
ms were not configured as part of this implementation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7e1b55e208c5">Operational validation was performed through:<=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac197bb1709b">
<li local-id=3D"fbedf04cd02e">
<p local-id=3D"7ea5120bed50">API endpoint testing via curl</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2c8adbe1b6e5">
<p local-id=3D"affd695811e3">Frontend functional validation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"460fc9ea41ee">
<p local-id=3D"60fbe58330ca">DynamoDB record verification</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ec8eb3e6ef02">
<p local-id=3D"fc59a7fd5f67">HTTPS validation checks</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a501e3fbcd31">System correctness was confirmed by observing =
successful data insertion into DynamoDB.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"2bff6fcbd5d0"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260302-204056.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"d75997658282a21baf468b26f7b485675216980955=
f5ef2f19c7357c8e743b56" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1818984526/image-20260302-204056.png?version=3D1&amp;=
modificationDate=3D1772484064179&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-he=
ight=3D"779" data-width=3D"1706" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-l=
inked-resource-id=3D"1822031898" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-li=
nked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"ima=
ge-20260302-204056.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki"=
 data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-conta=
iner-id=3D"1818984526" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3" data-me=
dia-id=3D"765cc98d-029f-4fae-87f1-15eda0905805" data-media-type=3D"file" he=
ight=3D"213"></span>
<p local-id=3D"a986f8321386">Figure 19: DynamoDB Entries Confirming Success=
ful Lambda Invocation</p>
<hr local-id=3D"deb5ed5330df">
<h3 local-id=3D"3a0c52d8cc19" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-VM-BasedMonitoring=
Approach">VM-Based Monitoring Approach</h3>
<p local-id=3D"efaa3b9c45be">Monitoring for the traditional deployment was =
performed using Linux service supervision and reverse proxy validation.</p>
<p local-id=3D"aa90033868b2">Service health validation methods included:</p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"22c2a73e3286">
<li local-id=3D"b90b568c02a5">
<p local-id=3D"bad8a801a2f1">systemd service status check for Gunicorn</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"6e747f66ebc2">
<p local-id=3D"81a750c6513c">Nginx configuration testing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39233868773b">
<p local-id=3D"b9b70958e9ad">Manual API endpoint testing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"01d72ccb8bf5">
<p local-id=3D"8df61743bcc7">SSL certificate verification</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f99a837bdacb">Primary operational command used:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo sy=
stemctl status powerofmath</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"20daefdf5728">This ensures:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"54eae26144b8">
<li local-id=3D"e25eeb559675">
<p local-id=3D"dbe3f1f405c4">Gunicorn running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6a4efdc6aba">
<p local-id=3D"c55b46cd7118">Workers active</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a982af63a70b">
<p local-id=3D"deb0c2e3dcc8">No runtime crashes</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9afeebc7532b"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
luence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260302-204133.png" width=
=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"eced373b7f53745c245a819fc4694326c3663a66bc=
cf31c482fcf30bb22c7a37" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki=
/download/attachments/1818984526/image-20260302-204133.png?version=3D1&amp;=
modificationDate=3D1772484101356&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-he=
ight=3D"521" data-width=3D"1706" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-l=
inked-resource-id=3D"1820557338" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-li=
nked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"ima=
