ight=3D"142"></span>
<p local-id=3D"528168794e09">Figure 20: Gunicorn Service Status Managed by =
systemd</p>
<hr local-id=3D"83f28458d9a7">
<h2 local-id=3D"d04aefcb6ad0" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-6.2AlertingandNoti=
fication">6.2 Alerting and Notification</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a5f001a4df81">Automated alerting mechanisms (CloudWatch Alar=
ms, SNS notifications) were not implemented due to project scope limitation=
s.</p>
<p local-id=3D"52a9cd6b58be">However, the architecture supports integration=
 with:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fb2db5ab4b0c">
<li local-id=3D"165b45303005">
<p local-id=3D"739838ef5a57">CloudWatch Alarms</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af58aa8b7a30">
<p local-id=3D"2ab9634597eb">SNS notifications</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1271f85eca1c">
<p local-id=3D"3e48e1be462c">Third-party monitoring systems</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3912162bdcb1">Manual verification was performed after each d=
eployment stage to confirm service health.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"5e63b1a6c2c2">
<h2 local-id=3D"9f2325301ae1" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentManagem=
ent">6.3 Incident Management</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8417e840c7c3">Incident handling followed structured troubles=
hooting steps.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"5237802eb0f3" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessTroubles=
hooting">Serverless Troubleshooting</h3>
<p local-id=3D"49c84970ed42">If issues occur:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"aa0a7ade0760">
<li local-id=3D"9f134ad97721">
<p local-id=3D"64b787357045">Validate API Gateway route</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aff1a16e0da1">
<p local-id=3D"a8edcb81472b">Verify Lambda permissions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f96a3091c373">
<p local-id=3D"1180593b92a3">Confirm DynamoDB access</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"61ad71f9a379" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-VM-BasedTroublesho=
oting">VM-Based Troubleshooting</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5c4abcd72fe1">If service failure occurs:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"09bdcfb5edcf">
<li local-id=3D"959d1e1441c4">
<p local-id=3D"a3e9727d0fbe">Check Gunicorn service status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2462bd151079">
<p local-id=3D"8b28aafc8341">Validate Nginx configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6d8ac40032ec">
<p local-id=3D"b270dc3f9a4b">Restart services if required</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"814dad6642cd">
<p local-id=3D"7fbb08b69b83">Verify SSL certificate validity</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3048625d8862">The use of systemd ensures service auto-restar=
t, improving resilience.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6ba9b0ec86da">
<h1 local-id=3D"7b95ec138e0e" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-7.Security&amp;Com=
pliance">7. Security &amp; Compliance</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"3bf3301d792a">
<h2 local-id=3D"32cb676d01b5" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-7.1InfrastructureS=
ecurity">7.1 Infrastructure Security</h2>
<p local-id=3D"62ccafd0e9ac">Security controls were implemented across both=
 architectures to ensure secure public exposure and protected backend servi=
ces.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e00f08263d4f">
<h3 local-id=3D"be143141b7d5" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessSecurity=
Controls">Serverless Security Controls</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"9ab30510d039">
<li local-id=3D"2905248b335f">
<p local-id=3D"d0a6da91c1bd">IAM Role-Based Access Control</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ade6bc2842fd">
<li local-id=3D"28ed8708d544">
<p local-id=3D"ad0f1cb02735">Lambda execution role with scoped permissions<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c9bdbd90ef4">
<p local-id=3D"f85c7aa63f7c">Access limited to required DynamoDB operations=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"37d140d5dc09">
<p local-id=3D"ecbe4ff70a61">No broad administrative privileges</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d8ed9970f80">
<p local-id=3D"c0815fef5483">HTTPS Enforcement</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fc20628eaf82">
<li local-id=3D"e4814db7ab87">
<p local-id=3D"83b4e3f4af96">SSL certificate issued via AWS ACM</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"001206949fdf">
<p local-id=3D"d61cd2d1fc7a">CloudFront configured with HTTPS-only access</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a48830bd8a0">
<p local-id=3D"4ded22083605">Secure communication between client and edge</=
p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"b5a7a16775cb">
<p local-id=3D"85769253a327">Managed Services Security</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed0cb3f11ca3">
<li local-id=3D"19f648a0187a">
<p local-id=3D"b742d71819a1">DynamoDB is serverless and not publicly access=
ible</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7bd303e6ad57">
<p local-id=3D"91e0ed683488">Lambda functions do not expose inbound ports</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1ffbddcc628f">
<p local-id=3D"4d10541bdd82">API Gateway controls request routing</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f402281bd73">
<p local-id=3D"565b0ca125e1">Principle of Least Privilege</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6f350d6b0af6">
<li local-id=3D"a506a0602041">
<p local-id=3D"d2007352b20e">IAM permissions restricted to necessary operat=
ions only</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"33db8cae563d">
<h3 local-id=3D"1afd0b1edfe5" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-TraditionalVM-Base=
dSecurityControls">Traditional VM-Based Security Controls</h3>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"efa12e4760ae">
<li local-id=3D"1c3ca816b81b">
<p local-id=3D"53b27fa9ae37">Security Group Firewall Rules</p>
<ul local-id=3D"77d6aa744bc7">
<li local-id=3D"898b9417b4e5">
<p local-id=3D"62894889a631">Only ports 22 (SSH), 80 (HTTP), and 443 (HTTPS=
) allowed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1da277ca70d4">
<p local-id=3D"9bc07292e258">No exposure of application port 5000</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"894ed8d3fce4">
<p local-id=3D"ba113223318f">No direct Gunicorn access from public internet=
</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"eae5b3c21035">
<p local-id=3D"1f0af9198334">Reverse Proxy Isolation</p>
<ul local-id=3D"001437cb23cf">
<li local-id=3D"bfe78088d262">
<p local-id=3D"8f87ccf8205a">Gunicorn bound to Unix socket</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"56517d6d5b55">
<p local-id=3D"c1654186586b">Nginx handles all external traffic</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f147705a9be1">
<p local-id=3D"6d460647c631">Backend not directly accessible</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7545fd4907b">
<p local-id=3D"3510a473b716">HTTPS Implementation</p>
<ul local-id=3D"52d4297aa5d0">
<li local-id=3D"a55d13368e87">
<p local-id=3D"2b01110f8eea">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt SSL certificate via Cert=
bot</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cfb073b9c4b">
<p local-id=3D"7087ec6621d7">Automatic renewal enabled</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1aaade1c5903">
<p local-id=3D"b3c30846e93c">HTTP redirected to HTTPS</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"b96ecf0186b6">
<p local-id=3D"c2b0b0e53c32">Service Management</p>
<ul local-id=3D"397cbf7e79cf">
<li local-id=3D"1c5b6f9e60b3">
<p local-id=3D"9b247098fa50">Gunicorn managed via systemd</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"242a616687cd">
<p local-id=3D"4fdb430a7aa2">Controlled restart and execution environment</=
p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"9a6b6396fe53"><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapp=
er image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conf=
