<p local-id=3D"dd6d890c1378"><br>
Figure 22: Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt Certificate Installed</p>
<hr local-id=3D"2f59a0b2709c">
<h2 local-id=3D"06e5b869abb9" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-7.2IdentityandAcce=
ssManagement(IAM)">7.2 Identity and Access Management (IAM)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"ce2d03f0f9db">IAM was implemented following AWS best practic=
es:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"13a0e4b1b8a3">
<li local-id=3D"b681da776dff">
<p local-id=3D"56db2553a21c">Role-based access for Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d055acf3a0ad">
<p local-id=3D"e018b6a0af0a">No embedded credentials in code</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f566ea94456c">
<p local-id=3D"f7e10c1d0626">No hardcoded secrets</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bef62c2e4ad">
<p local-id=3D"5db0cd27f67a">AWS-managed service permissions used</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"67779d4a144e">Access to EC2 was restricted via:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9e364c33c1d2">
<li local-id=3D"5d7d781ff355">
<p local-id=3D"24d6d283d043">Key pair-based SSH authentication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7185d0445406">
<p local-id=3D"efa7c2c24461">No password-based login</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8b7dee308017">This ensures controlled administrative access.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"bc10ff6e96b1">
<h2 local-id=3D"f46fa7dfdc1e" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-7.3ComplianceConsi=
derations">7.3 Compliance Considerations</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f13ddab35417">While this deployment was not subject to forma=
l regulatory compliance requirements (e.g., HIPAA, PCI-DSS), the following =
best practices were followed:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dc36a8f4c65c">
<li local-id=3D"b9bb92ac27a8">
<p local-id=3D"92c29fa9737c">Encrypted HTTPS communication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"79dfd5c3e39e">
<p local-id=3D"cbdadc995673">No plaintext credential storage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ec438fd8a05">
<p local-id=3D"27ba0194cc2d">Controlled firewall access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"598fd44019cb">
<p local-id=3D"0d84691ae560">Secure service isolation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c95f41c2d841">
<p local-id=3D"c3251d35b54d">Managed SSL certificate lifecycle</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"53611c402180">The solution is structured to support addition=
al compliance enhancements if required.</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"9f74f545a9f4" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimization=
">8. Cost Optimization</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"741641862605">
<h1 local-id=3D"54063c4b990b" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-8.1CostModelOvervi=
ew">8.1 Cost Model Overview</h1>
<p local-id=3D"7ae982cbdae3">The solution was designed with cost-efficiency=
 as a primary objective, leveraging AWS Free Tier resources and pay-per-use=
 services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6202df306f46">Two cost models were implemented:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"43341f1cee62">
<li local-id=3D"5915f9426291">
<p local-id=3D"fb3dbbb003b2">Serverless Pay-Per-Execution Model</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f93d6597499e">
<p local-id=3D"5b87777b46f3">Fixed Compute VM-Based Model</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"3ef03a93707d">This dual approach enables cost comparison bet=
ween elastic and persistent compute architectures.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"f402b74b8331">
<h1 local-id=3D"12d1abceb344" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-8.2DescriptionofCo=
stInputs">8.2 Description of Cost Inputs</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"5ff08c58d8e1" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessCostInpu=
ts">Serverless Cost Inputs</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b112f0eef955">Services Used:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c3ae2e523598">
<li local-id=3D"2181e33517a3">
<p local-id=3D"0ee2b144bc16">AWS Lambda (pay per invocation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f426ab176b0f">
<p local-id=3D"cf58e0bebec2">API Gateway (per request pricing)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ad579cc6ddf3">
<p local-id=3D"57010139afe1">DynamoDB (on-demand billing)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0a5ae35421f">
<p local-id=3D"c89e4c9df15d">S3 (storage + requests)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6d0602e0bf7">
<p local-id=3D"75596dc17bac">CloudFront (data transfer + requests)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"10fcb767826d">
<p local-id=3D"1ffa779196b9">ACM (free for AWS services)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f3ca37fc9587">Cost Characteristics:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7cfa5753c290">
<li local-id=3D"4bd4811c44ed">
<p local-id=3D"ac8ffb3c44f8">No fixed compute cost</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e04847b6f2dc">
<p local-id=3D"40a8d40e0f1a">Pay only for actual usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"347bd70acf02">
<p local-id=3D"670979f9e7fd">Zero cost during idle periods</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2e15763c7b3">
<p local-id=3D"e8ea2dfb20cf">Automatically scales with traffic</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e08fa534ff56">
<h2 local-id=3D"f17dd4d8b302" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-VM-BasedCostInputs=
">VM-Based Cost Inputs</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a0267de3d34d">Services Used:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"10374da3493d">
<li local-id=3D"4999422500a5">
<p local-id=3D"39dc75975e16">EC2 Instance (fixed hourly cost)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"38de31ed2cf8">
<p local-id=3D"626fda0798e3">Elastic IP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"76525f5d6651">
<p local-id=3D"1d8b7e65ae77">Data transfer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21db2a8d5515">
<p local-id=3D"697f5f2e981f">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt (free SSL)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ab4f73c7150d">Cost Characteristics:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"aa852a7732bf">
<li local-id=3D"f3a96142f9ac">
<p local-id=3D"1c6a006cf472">Fixed compute cost regardless of traffic</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"c5e738b3ac97">
<p local-id=3D"a818f951ac96">Manual scaling required</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bdcb0f76f786">
<p local-id=3D"57a0aa2b9664">Resource utilization may be low during idle ti=
me</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"283dc15cbbbc">
<h1 local-id=3D"ab535e228edc" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-8.3SummaryofCostMo=
del">8.3 Summary of Cost Model</h1>
<p local-id=3D"64e00819a743">Serverless Architecture:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"52c245720821">
<li local-id=3D"c156297ca526">
<p local-id=3D"481ed2b86949">Lower operational overhead</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a3887c79ace">
<p local-id=3D"20bbfddc2626">Cost-efficient for unpredictable workloads</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"128e63cd2974">
<p local-id=3D"93b4c402657a">Scales automatically</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"040e4e092846">
<p local-id=3D"da685489765c">No infrastructure management cost</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aca2f00d5b3b">VM-Based Architecture:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fdbed109ff5e">
<li local-id=3D"6ba5d09523f9">
<p local-id=3D"3c52e341d406">Predictable monthly compute cost</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a72f02fdb9d2">
<p local-id=3D"3ef4179a4530">Higher operational responsibility</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e576f9aa9177">
<p local-id=3D"15b7e749d72b">Better suited for constant workload scenarios<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b5739642a16">
<p local-id=3D"ef7f6277ca0b">Requires capacity planning</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c8da4dda6d24">
<h1 local-id=3D"0028d6666225" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-8.4BusinessValueAn=
alysis">8.4 Business Value Analysis</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c976187b8589">From a business perspective, the serverless ar=
chitecture provides:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e51a4526977b">
<li local-id=3D"d942358d34ca">
<p local-id=3D"80766b8d9f46">Reduced infrastructure management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dbf8810ec5b">
<p local-id=3D"2efb31ba88ef">Faster deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"99672b1d7a0b">
<p local-id=3D"5c0659bf535d">Automatic scalability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9c1aa41e0b6">
<p local-id=3D"5e1d9376bbae">Lower operational risk</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"649368fd47da">The VM-based architecture provides:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bd5410aa30f0">
<li local-id=3D"4326fa6de497">
<p local-id=3D"22937c952844">Full system-level control</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7eb781baea0c">
<p local-id=3D"4327889de187">Custom runtime optimization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d47e55833f2a">
<p local-id=3D"52d809132e45">Greater flexibility for complex workloads</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"484660551048">This implementation enables decision-makers to=
 evaluate:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"860ac99b19f8">
<li local-id=3D"b03dbe3108fe">
<p local-id=3D"82e469c33931">Elastic cost model vs fixed cost model</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"94f4d5c4e7f6">
<p local-id=3D"10449d242bf0">Managed services vs infrastructure ownership</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1955278cc511">
<p local-id=3D"3b5c2f476535">Scalability vs control trade-offs</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f73cdaf695a8">
<h1 local-id=3D"274e1d71c90b" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-8.5Right-Sizing&am=
p;OptimizationDecisions">8.5 Right-Sizing &amp; Optimization Decisions</h1>
<p local-id=3D"6566268f1389">Cost optimization decisions included:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"edfcd40c7add">
<li local-id=3D"6f304b187d96">
<p local-id=3D"a41f3da38a7e">Using free-tier EC2 instance</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc716fbbc65f">
<p local-id=3D"c3fea8798294">On-demand DynamoDB billing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"667f53443466">
<p local-id=3D"3c61d682e720">Avoiding over-provisioned compute</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"908abaed1987">
<p local-id=3D"9d88200556b6">Using serverless where applicable</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"156505c7769f">
<p local-id=3D"8a0d1d8a8761">Using managed SSL solutions (ACM &amp; Let=E2=
=80=99s Encrypt)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"abac028c19a4">
<p local-id=3D"93cbe110ab52">No unused AWS resources provisioned</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"ed2bc3dce4d7" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-10.ImplementationT=
imeline">10. Implementation Timeline</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"3cf99f819805">
<h2 local-id=3D"0ac74cca6fa4" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-10.1MilestonesandD=
eliverables">10.1 Milestones and Deliverables</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5a59b20d1934">The project was completed within a structured =
5-hour execution window as per assignment requirements.</p>
<p local-id=3D"83a3d557b79b">The implementation was divided into logical ph=
ases to ensure controlled deployment and validation.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c85745f03294">
<h3 local-id=3D"fd9a2088cce4" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-Phase1:Requirement=
Analysis&amp;ArchitectureDesign">Phase 1: Requirement Analysis &amp; Archit=
ecture Design</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"41baf362f213">
<li local-id=3D"85728203baca">
<p local-id=3D"2a269f627039">Reviewed repository and application structure<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed04ab15cb90">
<p local-id=3D"f5c157aadcd4">Identified frontend and backend components</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"eae4340d4d9c">
<p local-id=3D"5f0add0f37a1">Designed Serverless and VM-based architecture<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13b3b34bb4a9">
<p local-id=3D"b6198b9edf16">Selected appropriate AWS services</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c75f0f3b6e06">
<p local-id=3D"c0e1c9e94cf7">Planned SSL implementation approach</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4f4b864de2fd">Deliverable:<br>
Architecture selection and deployment strategy finalized</p>
<hr local-id=3D"02099ae2187c">
<h3 local-id=3D"9a9504c0446a" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-Phase2:ServerlessD=
eploymentImplementation">Phase 2: Serverless Deployment Implementation</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ff1e50754e27">Activities:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4fb7e4f0fff4">
<li local-id=3D"5c4c689fa8ce">
<p local-id=3D"1a38d7a7936c">Created IAM role for Lambda execution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d20368b7b8b">
<p local-id=3D"4bd0ab42f60a">Configured DynamoDB table</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bfaaaaab4356">
<p local-id=3D"0a7bf3b21e74">Developed and deployed Lambda function</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"776653cca7a8">
<p local-id=3D"bf913f0bb343">Configured API Gateway integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc9427b22e73">
<p local-id=3D"ce0191648eb2">Implemented CORS handling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e9b653646ed">
<p local-id=3D"317dd72e4b40">Hosted frontend on S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16332612ca12">
<p local-id=3D"76729e400b8c">Configured CloudFront distribution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1516e432ecf6">
<p local-id=3D"039bd467b6a1">Requested SSL certificate via ACM</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"434f7fbdb067">
<p local-id=3D"ba2a41e3a414">Validated public HTTPS endpoint</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e75188941d3b">Deliverable:<br>
Fully functional serverless architecture with HTTPS access</p>
<hr local-id=3D"55f6edde486d">
<h3 local-id=3D"4da984470a7a" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-Phase3:Traditional=
VM-BasedDeployment">Phase 3: Traditional VM-Based Deployment</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ac8a45903dc0">Activities:</p>
