<li local-id=3D"f0093c48d170">
<p local-id=3D"fc0d50200cc1">Verified service persistence after restart</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e0d8fbaf0e54">Deliverable:<br>
Production-grade EC2 deployment with HTTPS and reverse proxy</p>
<hr local-id=3D"d6f1ad323373">
<h3 local-id=3D"0300d5f86ff0" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-Phase4:Validation&=
amp;SecurityHardening">Phase 4: Validation &amp; Security Hardening</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1d20a29a3339">Activities:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"69b1c7a4052d">
