<p local-id=3D"03411da3d264">Verified backend isolation (Unix socket bindin=
g)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eb07c15a5646">
<p local-id=3D"56cc46fc8253">Validated no public exposure of internal ports=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"860c463a9c68">
<p local-id=3D"c7623d81ef89">Confirmed SSL certificates active</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa5a5012b63d">
<p local-id=3D"a65582a2cf6a">Confirmed DNS resolution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fcbb6e39f1a">
<p local-id=3D"0bd5d1df81d7">Tested application end-to-end</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f4444cc388c4">Deliverable:<br>
Secure and publicly accessible deployments</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e7c0f2bec647">
