<li local-id=3D"a8abcee504f0">
<p local-id=3D"dad29ebf3ce5">Documented security and cost analysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e30e234e6d2b">
<p local-id=3D"c95ff7cea162">Compared Serverless vs VM-based architecture</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ecac1b0aa612">
<p local-id=3D"7ae09ace6f9f">Structured implementation timeline</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"82e2eb0bb456">Deliverable:<br>
Client-grade technical documentation</p>
