<h1 local-id=3D"86595ed66764" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousImpro=
vement">11. Continuous Improvement</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"51663b7d54ef">
<h2 local-id=3D"b23ce740b4c0" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-11.1FeedbackandRet=
rospectives">11.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2eeb2874898e">The deployment process was reviewed after comp=
letion to identify improvement opportunities across architecture, security,=
 and operational efficiency.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7c7ec08fb0da">Feedback areas considered:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8fd597f27c20">
<li local-id=3D"b29931e69fe8">
<p local-id=3D"0f5b4b433956">Deployment speed and complexity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"724c9ae7a99c">
<p local-id=3D"58faddfec272">Security hardening scope</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ab7ebad2f3d3">
<p local-id=3D"c82b2d4bdbce">Monitoring maturity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d934f30134bc">
<p local-id=3D"cbbf0fb9ba8c">Automation gaps</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ccac9c3d17b2">
<p local-id=3D"a576ddcb828c">Cost visibility</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fddbbd4813c2">Key Observations:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"afe0ffd22975">
<li local-id=3D"ab84d8d8d31a">
<p local-id=3D"b617ee8ab42b">Serverless deployment required fewer operation=
al steps but more IAM precision.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8d9d1c81338">
<p local-id=3D"93b74b920f4d">VM-based deployment required deeper system-lev=
el configuration.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8734a21db814">
<p local-id=3D"05c2de09ed94">Reverse proxy configuration added stability an=
d security benefits.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05c91b7c4a9b">
<p local-id=3D"e84200cb1cfc">DNS propagation and SSL validation introduced =
real-world production complexity.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d70e161c36e8">Future retrospectives would include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0192c017b24b">
<li local-id=3D"b5833599a7e0">
<p local-id=3D"a55d0f3d0492">Automated deployment scripts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d6722b4969bf">
<p local-id=3D"5ffd20e78dec">Infrastructure-as-Code implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"071c13420763">
<p local-id=3D"88a0b1c7c606">CI/CD pipeline integration</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9dca02058910">
<h2 local-id=3D"d83bbb69ad62" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-11.2IterativeEnhan=
cements">11.2 Iterative Enhancements</h2>
<p local-id=3D"8e38a864ee02">Although the deployment met all assignment req=
uirements, the architecture is designed to evolve.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cdec699ac6d6">Potential enhancements include:</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"8b83970ba660" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ServerlessImprovem=
ents">Serverless Improvements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4113b4dbedea">
<li local-id=3D"044b255c5306">
<p local-id=3D"e67d6ad9459a">Implement CloudWatch Alarms for Lambda errors<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6f501795b45">
<p local-id=3D"500140ea9ae3">Add API Gateway throttling policies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9818c283fab">
<p local-id=3D"94c7c012d0ef">Introduce WAF for enhanced edge security</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"1c1c578d2aa6">
<p local-id=3D"7d4b5bea7a18">Configure logging dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4539b5f958a9">
<p local-id=3D"2a18b5bd53a0">Implement infrastructure using AWS CDK or Terr=
aform</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3fb2e0e557d9">
<h3 local-id=3D"0ddae28b211f" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-VM-BasedImprovemen=
ts">VM-Based Improvements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"dbb979c15515">
<li local-id=3D"247096f7df63">
<p local-id=3D"94917b6b24c9">Containerize application using Docker</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44d26aa63cd5">
<p local-id=3D"2b11a9ed7a7e">Implement Nginx rate limiting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b7935379955">
<p local-id=3D"73aae442400e">Add automated log rotation and analysis</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"edac8bd21562">
<p local-id=3D"1d2b56941e4d">Introduce CI/CD pipeline for code deployment</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"20f02baeaed2">
<p local-id=3D"79a82b104b2f">Add monitoring using Prometheus + Grafana</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7b58c1ed34e7">
<h3 local-id=3D"33cae507ad58" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ScalabilityEnhance=
ments">Scalability Enhancements</h3>
<p local-id=3D"eb4aa0b48ec3">Serverless architecture can scale automaticall=
y.</p>
<p local-id=3D"324c967aba3d">For VM-based deployment, scaling improvements =
could include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7b834e895b17">
<li local-id=3D"bcb3aaa7a438">
<p local-id=3D"3ca686d0500d">Load Balancer integration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc6811837b2d">
<p local-id=3D"8a8b230d7502">Auto Scaling Group configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f351fa18150a">
<p local-id=3D"564202120f25">Blue-Green deployment strategy</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7efb05b3397b">
<h3 local-id=3D"6bcdde1ee5b5" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-CostOptimizationEn=
hancements">Cost Optimization Enhancements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a83aa8f83183">
<li local-id=3D"398556110e70">
<p local-id=3D"577859a86bb5">Enable detailed billing alerts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48e532acd173">
<p local-id=3D"7e85d25db79f">Analyze CloudFront traffic patterns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ac75d6efa99c">
<p local-id=3D"3363c442271d">Evaluate reserved instances if traffic stabili=
zes</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"513b94456b95">
<h2 local-id=3D"8266b3f88a2b" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-ContinuousMaturity=
Vision">Continuous Maturity Vision</h2>
<p local-id=3D"93905de2b079">The project demonstrates foundational DevOps i=
mplementation across two architectural models.</p>
<p local-id=3D"21c36760ff93">Future maturity stages could include:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"acdf706e9075">
<li local-id=3D"07954de68b67">
<p local-id=3D"0c0819b41730">Full Infrastructure-as-Code adoption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbfb1c163bf5">
<p local-id=3D"b5584c0f4735">Zero-downtime deployments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"190161ef2d56">
<p local-id=3D"b991c3a404be">Automated rollback strategies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e8f100adcbbd">
<p local-id=3D"380c7234e0e1">Observability dashboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e73672e7198">
<p local-id=3D"a2664f1bd282">Security scanning integration</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"d1bb7e7c4f64" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion">12.=
 Conclusion</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"abe269499f4e">
<h2 local-id=3D"7fc211a7a5cd" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-12.1Summary">12.1 =
Summary</h2>
<p local-id=3D"2246edb6c6b7">This project successfully implemented and depl=
oyed the <strong>PowerOfMath application</strong> using two distinct archit=
ectural approaches on AWS Cloud:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"fe8a1d0244ad">
<li local-id=3D"564387f34d39">
<p local-id=3D"332b9407ea62">Serverless Architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4c2dbe20a0d">
<p local-id=3D"dc01d9ce3ef8">Traditional VM-Based Architecture</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e7888e039a8f">The serverless deployment leveraged:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7366d6f86ca1">
<li local-id=3D"608a3ed46121">
<p local-id=3D"4f4be67a530c">AWS Lambda</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e707b0074530">
<p local-id=3D"e3d56d5fcb32">API Gateway</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6764b817a5a0">
<p local-id=3D"ade96641ed9c">DynamoDB</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"12dd941e26a9">
<p local-id=3D"bf4ef1fe1e78">S3 Static Hosting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0b12e8aef41">
<p local-id=3D"51f84549eefd">CloudFront</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a177b64d42ca">
<p local-id=3D"56f4ecb2844b">AWS ACM for SSL</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d44dc01b04b5">This model demonstrated:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7621dd408629">
<li local-id=3D"f59a39432ff6">
<p local-id=3D"db1fc345ad77">Automatic scaling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ccb05e19218">
<p local-id=3D"2a8e4b2a44d5">Pay-per-use cost efficiency</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e313e7b235de">
<p local-id=3D"074efee24e06">Reduced infrastructure management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67640ee39e7f">
<p local-id=3D"3c7f3c310c35">Fully managed service architecture</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8bff6546be43">The traditional deployment utilized:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"cf5ee3fe1b6e">
<li local-id=3D"bcbe58f36c97">
<p local-id=3D"81fe0e42816d">Amazon EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"956478dbf269">
<p local-id=3D"7e93fd6f5e19">Gunicorn (WSGI Server)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4ce5918ad232">
<p local-id=3D"a294e64b022d">Nginx Reverse Proxy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"edda425533ae">
<p local-id=3D"0452a94bfdb2">systemd Service Management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa438c804ad8">
<p local-id=3D"d608896bfa07">Let=E2=80=99s Encrypt SSL</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4f7b96a20144">This model demonstrated:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"57560532d96c">
<li local-id=3D"d4de12149555">
<p local-id=3D"ebf7dc5dd858">Full infrastructure control</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"441a0a0258f5">
<p local-id=3D"3cbcb95e0b74">Manual scaling capability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"029c79731299">
<p local-id=3D"f09ffd820bc4">Production-grade reverse proxy setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3f64d023845">
<p local-id=3D"4d6082860d8f">Service persistence and system-level monitorin=
g</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"4bcc07fd6996">Both environments were secured using HTTPS and=
 validated with proper DNS configuration.</p>
<p local-id=3D"626f29d745e5">The project fulfilled all functional and secur=
ity requirements within the defined time window.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"abb37389710e">
<h2 local-id=3D"96df3ea13bee" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-12.2NextSteps">12.=
2 Next Steps</h2>
<p local-id=3D"326ee7f28382">To further enhance the architecture, the follo=
wing improvements are recommended:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e1866c9ad7a5">
<li local-id=3D"1cf2cb86170a">
<p local-id=3D"605491a33a84">Implement Infrastructure as Code (Terraform / =
AWS CDK)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2b737f2f9c6">
<p local-id=3D"d6feb2e62206">Introduce CI/CD pipelines for automated deploy=
ments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7179fbd1d3de">
<p local-id=3D"31f2e2fc9a26">Configure CloudWatch alarms and monitoring das=
hboards</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7458b2dedd3">
<p local-id=3D"7f76ace1411e">Add Load Balancer + Auto Scaling for VM archit=
ecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"868376baa26f">
<p local-id=3D"48ea339a11a3">Implement WAF for edge-level security</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bf81e4e1875">
<p local-id=3D"7ca69908aa2c">Introduce containerization (Docker) for portab=
ility</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ccbac38ccaba">These improvements would elevate the solution =
from a deployment implementation to a production-ready DevOps pipeline arch=
itecture.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"fb05c2a65481" id=3D"T9-TechnicalDocument-13.CustomerAcknowl=
edgement">13. Customer Acknowledgement</h2>
<p local-id=3D"4e0db66f4fc0"><strong>Name:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"2255c610e0cf"><strong>Title:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"ee1a8be78283"><strong>Signature:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"9002595d1331"><strong>Date:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"1009fdbde945">&nbsp;</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
